title: Maui Jim Coral Mens Sunglasses 2492M Overview
description:
Maui Jim Black and Grey Mens Sunglasses - 249-2M - http://www.abt.com/product/67822/Maui-Jim-2492M.html

Features:

Perfect for: Whatever you want to do as this is a very versatile style — lens treatments and frames are saltwater safe
Design: A contemporary twist on a clean classic look featuring stylish double bar at the temples
Shape: Refined rectangular frame complements a range of facial shapes
Care: Maui Jim case and cleaning cloth included
Neutral Grey: Perfect for especially bright direct sunlight. Offers rich color and contrast along with the highest available light production unlike ordinary grey lenses that flatten light evenly across the spectrum.
FRAME
Material: Monel metal an extremely strong corrosion-resistant alloy with acetate temple tips
Finishing Treatment: Matte finish on frame front; high-gloss on temples
Hinge: Anti-corrosive spring that provides flexibility offering a secure comfortable fit for various face shapes and sizes
Bridge: Saddle style single-bridge with non-slip adjustable Rabalon nose pads
